{"tid":2202104,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[不意外］知乎網友發現 華為既鴻蒙2.0 係直接copy Android","createTime":"2020-09-14T10:12:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T05:34:08.000Z","uid":48083,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"550ff95fe30d5408baab816aa4acf4b649e51b81","tid":2202104,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T10:12:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/shinchven/status/1304297452359491584?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fshinchven%2Fstatus%2F1304297452359491584%3Fs%3D21&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacfsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=b86d76f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fshinchven%2Fstatus%2F1304297452359491584%3Fs%3D21&h=18f4c35e\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/shinchven/status/1304297452359491584?s=21</a><br />\n<em><br />\n一夜之間就能啓用鴻蒙，現有手機能立刻升級。我們always ready。<br />\n<br />\n不謙虛地說，我們可以一夜之間，將所有手機都升級到鴻蒙。<br />\n<br />\n鴻蒙系統速度比安卓快60%。<br />\n<br />\n安卓已經被鴻蒙掏空。<br />\n<br />\nP40已經完全沒有谷歌的東西了，海外在陸續鋪貨。</em><br />\n<br />\n結果最後版本號2.0的竟然還是beta，我也算是大開眼界。<br />\n<br />\n2016年的LiteOS翻出來縫合一下安卓，成了，2.0！<br />\n<br />\n吹的吊打A公司和G公司的五大獨有特性一個沒見著。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n按照當初2007年安卓以實機demo開源時、一周後就能發佈sdk，以這個完成度為標桿，目前鴻蒙OS完成度大概有6%。而在2019年8月9日的開發者大會發佈該PPTOS時，其完成度只有1%。<br />\n<br />\n也即是說要達到2007年安卓開源時的完成度，以華為一年零一個月的進展只有5%來看，鴻蒙OS開源完成需要20年。<br />\n<br />\n嗯，有進步，可喜可賀。[驚喜]<br />\n<br />\n所以沸騰的外行奔走相告大聲疾呼「打臉了」的底氣從何而來？？<em><br />\n<br />\n「雖然我不懂技術，但是現在你們這些質疑按揭開源的終於被打臉了，哈哈哈哈」</em><br />\n被迫承認按揭開源？被迫承認因為按揭開源的PPTOS，所以被打了一年零一個月的臉？<br />\n<br />\n之前號稱研發投入一年近1500億。<br />\n<em><br />\n任正非之前在內部透露的信息顯示，華為計劃把2020年研發預算提高58億美元，而今年他們的整個研發費用要超過200億美元的水平，約合人民幣超1421億元。</em><br />\n而在鴻蒙上這一年投入了上億。<br />\n<em><br />\n我們開始構築自己的生態，把生態乾起來，鴻蒙系統已經投入上億，體驗一直在改善，現在能達到安卓70-80%水平，但是每天每周每個月都在改進。<br />\n以區區一億研發投入的鴻蒙OS，就達到了安卓70-80%的水平，並且速度比安卓快60%，這鴻蒙OS是何等的黑科技啊？</em><br />\n<br />\n然後今天就這？？<br />\n<br />\n憋了一年零一個月，可算是給憋壞了吧？<br />\n<br />\n不過也沒事，等川普大選完了，萬一制裁結束了呢？就不需要商用鴻蒙OS了，虛幻的氣泡也就沒人去戳破了。<br />\n<br />\n那萬一制裁沒結束，持續時間超過華為自己的時間表從而不得不發佈鴻蒙OS的手機，到時又怎麼辦呢？<br />\n<br />\n嗨，這還不簡單，抄智慧屏的作業不就是了。我說這是鴻蒙OS1.0的電視，這就是鴻蒙OS1.0的電視；我說這是鴻蒙OS2.0的手機，這就是鴻蒙OS2.0的手機。<br />\n<br />\n你們質疑者還能咋滴？我車庫里就是有一條看不見碰不著的噴火龍，咋滴？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再拖個三五年，七八年，總能擼個幾百萬行獨有核心代碼的鴻蒙OS出來了。到時候就又可以跳出說「哈哈哈，終於打質疑者的臉了。」<br />\n<br />\n沒事的，時間多，反正隔三差五沸騰一回，也不耽誤賣手機賣各種終端不是？？<br />\n<br />\n至於此時這些突然冒出來叫囂「終於打臉了」的一行代碼都沒寫過的外行人，那是萬萬不會和我們質疑者結算過去一年多來「按揭開源欠下的債」，只會暫且退避，他朝開個三無新小號，又是一條沸騰好漢。"},{"pid":"21ab8caf3865621a36f24293b04a04d2f48f1369","tid":2202104,"uid":48083,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T10:16:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WKnEheT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWKnEheT.png&h=5375847b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m4vZheW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm4vZheW.png&h=0e851f09&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xj7HZti.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXj7HZti.png&h=c83acdfc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M1ane1G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM1ane1G.png&h=980642ce&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4NwQ8mH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4NwQ8mH.png&h=18a0fd8a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8364fbc6b3778b948013b6ff15a34422c73d82ed","tid":2202104,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T10:30:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0166d655eed85981548b12c83022f22b4df2991","tid":2202104,"uid":266391,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T10:34:02.000Z","msg":"利害了，我的國<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n比人封殺唔好問點解啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"263365ce9a044d36d012f998fdd7a20f7c389e77","tid":2202104,"uid":38192,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T10:35:17.000Z","msg":"Powered by Android"},{"pid":"d7fe4cbe3094f3ee5e3516924b32219bb8239c12","tid":2202104,"uid":214173,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T10:39:24.000Z","msg":"到Android出版本更新佢仲生唔生存到?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7110aa76aacfc42c4dc952509f58aded53d4ec20","tid":2202104,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T10:40:01.000Z","msg":"唔準干預支那手機既設定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4d7bdce91ab38ef0c6e01c5ffc017f6c4612c09","tid":2202104,"uid":49370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T10:43:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad30d4677fd6481637fee5988311f635c79b3d0e","tid":2202104,"uid":288304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d7fe4cbe3094f3ee5e3516924b32219bb8239c12","tid":2202104,"uid":214173,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T10:39:24.000Z","msg":"到Android出版本更新佢仲生唔生存到?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T10:46:06.000Z","msg":"佢咪remark個version number<br />\n<br />\nUI 改下次序Grouping，將D本來用緊的野變成新function"},{"pid":"47fc126bede0a7123e2b31c856bf4209b6efbe0b","tid":2202104,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T10:46:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43358ceeacfc6f8fd5122bb9a0f987a227340b6e","tid":2202104,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7fe4cbe3094f3ee5e3516924b32219bb8239c12","tid":2202104,"uid":214173,"like":2,"dislik